DTSTART:20260723T000000Z
DESCRIPTION:Murray & Peter Present: "The Marvelous Miss Gender" starring BO
	SCO. From RuPaul's Drag Race Season 14\, 2022 and most recently All Stars 
	10 from 2025\, BOSCO is now headlining her first ever solo tour. Meet & Gr
	eet add-on tickets are sold separately. To attend the M&G\, fans must also
	 purchase a ticket to the event. Show starts at 8pm. There will be a 20-mi
